headline: Healthpeak Properties, Inc. Announces Public Filing of Registration Statement with the SEC for Janus Living, Inc.
summary: DENVER, February 27, 2026--Healthpeak Properties, Inc. (NYSE: DOC) today announced that Janus Living, Inc., a pure-play senior housing real estate investment trust ("REIT"), has publicly filed a registration statement on Form S-11 with the Securities and Exchange Commission (the "SEC") relating to a proposed initial public offering of its shares of Class A-1 common stock.
